http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Girl-ends-life-parents-suspect-murder/article13979302.ece

In a suspected suicide pact, a 14-year-old girl died and her 22-year-old boyfriend’s condition is serious after the duo allegedly consumed rat poison in Mandya on Sunday. However, the victim’s parents alleged that the boy might have forced their daughter to commit suicide and filed a complaint.The police said the victim eloped and married her neighbour, Kishore, recently. Her parents managed to trace her and left her at their ancestral house, from where she went missing the next day. The duo went to Kishore’s mother’s residence in Mandya. However, they decided to end their lives after the victim’s parents tracked them down.